==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Finalist
<hw>Fi"nal*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Sports)</fld>
<def>Any of the players who meet in the final round of a tournament in
which the losers in any round do not play again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Finality</ent>⟦br⟧
